data.description: Want the perfect lot with all the additional parking your heart could desire? Then, this house is your dream home! With a large 2 car garage and a carport for another 2 cars, the corner lot even offers a 2nd driveway with COVERED RV PARKING in the back! The home interior is cozy and offers 3 bedrooms with the most beautiful closet doors. (Seriously, I know that is a weird thing to mention in the description but, it is true!) The backyard also offers a covered patio and a below the ground 15 person storm shelter, and the crowning jewel: 3 producing pecan trees! Award winning elementary school is within walking distance. This home would bring in roughly $1150/month in income, just in case you are interested in this property for an investment.
